    public class PreferenceActivity
extends AppCompatActivity
implements View.OnClickListener
    OK so why is here? Stupid reason #1: Android Studio's wizard generates a bunch of stupid complex code Stupid reason #2: Android's Preference Activity is API10+ and we (osmdroid) are API8+ Stupid reason #3: Simple is better, usually
    Since:
    5.6 Created by alex on 10/21/16.
